snippet: Chinese internet service provider Tencent Holdings plans to acquire an 11.3 percent stake in digital mapping service provider Navinfo Co Ltd for 1.17 billion yuan ($187.33 million), Navinfo said late on Monday....

headline.print_headline: China's Tencent Plans to Acquire Stake in Map Provider Navinfo
headline.main: China's Tencent Plans to Acquire Stake in Map Provider Navinfo

lead_paragraph: Chinese internet service provider Tencent Holdings plans to acquire an 11.3 percent stake in digital mapping service provider Navinfo Co Ltd for 1.17 billion yuan ($187.33 million), Navinfo said late on Monday.
